servicedefinition.description: Using SNMP, this service monitors the status of a RAID Controller in a Fujitsu server.

moduleparameter.help: The number of minutes between scans.

Enter the name of the RAID Controller to be monitored.

For a list of RAID Controllers, query the device with the 1.3.6.1.4.1.231.2.49.1.4.2.1.25 SNMP OID.
